		{"id":"n_task","type":"text","text":"## task 工具\n\n父端特有\n子端无此工具","x":220,"y":-300,"width":200,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_recursive","type":"text","text":"## 禁止递归\n\n不是技术限制\n防止目标偏移\n防止成本失控","x":0,"y":50,"width":200,"height":100,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_recursive_tradeoff","type":"text","text":"扁平 vs 层级权衡\n顶层控制 vs 层层传递","x":0,"y":180,"width":200,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_safety","type":"text","text":"## safety_limit\n\n30轮兜底\n防无限循环\n不是项目大小判断","x":220,"y":50,"width":200,"height":100,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_next","type":"text","text":"## 后续课程\n\nL05 Skill Loading → Subagent 加载 Skill\nL06 Context Compact → Subagent 摘要策略\nL09 Agent Teams → 多 Subagent 协作","x":0,"y":300,"width":600,"height":100,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"n_return","type":"text","text":"## 返回值机制\n\n最后一次 text\n不是 tool_use","x":440,"y":-300,"width":200,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"n_return_detail","type":"text","text":"中间过程全部丢弃\n只保留语义摘要","x":440,"y":-180,"width":200,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_control","type":"text","text":"## 控制权归属\n\n父端控制决策\n子端执行任务","x":440,"y":50,"width":200,"height":80,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"n_control_soft","type":"text","text":"软返回约定\n子端返回 text\n父端收到 tool_result","x":440,"y":180,"width":200,"height":60,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"n_proc_thread","type":"text","text":"## 进程 vs 线程\n\n进程：独立内存\n线程：共享内存\nSubagent：独立 messages","x":640,"y":-300,"width":220,"height":100,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_unix_llm","type":"text","text":"## Unix vs LLM\n\nUnix：无损传输\nLLM：有损压缩\n只保留语义摘要","x":640,"y":-160,"width":220,"height":100,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_boss_worker","type":"text","text":"## 老板 vs 员工\n\n老板派活\n员工干活\n只汇报结果","x":640,"y":-20,"width":220,"height":80,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"n_code","type":"text","text":"## 核心代码\n\n```python\ndef run_subagent(prompt):\n    sub_messages = [{role: user, content: prompt}]\n    for _ in range(30):  # safety_limit\n        response = client.messages.create(\n            messages=sub_messages,\n            tools=CHILD_TOOLS  # 无 task\n        )\n        if stop_reason != tool_use:\n            break\n    return b.text for b in response  # 只取 text\n```\n\n**关键行**: 干净上下文 + 禁止递归 + 只返回 text","x":640,"y":100,"width":420,"height":180,"color":"1"},
